General.Name: Hoffmen Cleanindo
General.Description: PT Hoffmen Cleanindo Tbk, through its subsidiaries, engages in the provision of facility management services. The company operates through Cleaning and Parking segments. It offers cleaning services, including indoor or outdoor cleanliness, tidiness, and hygienization of office rooms, toilets, and hallways, as well as in the courtyards, lobbies, and surrounding areas. The company also provides garden maintenance services comprising cleaning the area, removing nuisance plants, applying fertilizer, and performing repairs to plants in malls, office buildings, hotels, factories, and others; window glass cleaning services; and marble and granite floor polishing services for office building, malls, or hotel floors. In addition, it provides air fresheners and cleaning fluids, such as aerosols, sanitary ware, and dispensers for restrooms; and offers labor supply services, including receptionist, technician, cashier, factory laborer, or office administration employees, as well as provides employee training services. Further, the company offers security services, such as security guard services for malls, office buildings, hotels, factories, and housing; and investigation support services for crimes occurred in malls, office buildings, hotels, and factories. Additionally, through its subsidiary, it is involved in the provision of parking management and valet services, parking guidance systems, access control and e-ticketing, and level parking and parking lifts solutions. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Jakarta Utara, Indonesia. PT Hoffmen Cleanindo Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Japarto Sukses Mandiri.
